            "body": "<p>Your log is not displaying because:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>            if(millisUntilFinished / 10000 == 0){ //TEN SECONDS\n                Log.v(TAG, (millisUntilFinished % 1000) + \" seconds left\");\n            }\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>you want it to display when you have 10000 millisUntilFinished but 10000/10000 = 1 not 0.<\/p>\n\n<p>it should be:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>     if(millisUntilFinished / 10000 == 1) || if(millisUntilFinished % 10000 == 0)\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>or simply:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>    if(millisUntilFinished == 10000)\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
